Referred to Committee on Ways and Means
SUMMARY—Makes appropriations to the Department of Public
Safety for the replacement of computer hardware,
equipment and associated software, vehicles and
furniture and for information technology projects
and a recruiting campaign. (BDR S-1213)
FISCAL NOTE: Effect on Local Government: No.
Effect on the State: Contains Appropriation not included
in Executive Budget.
